description:
In this presentation, we look at martial arts and spirituality. Many think of martial arts as providing useful self-defence skills, a good way to become physically fit, and a way to improve confidence. But few consider the spiritual element. Yet, martial arts and spirituality are closely linked. Many martial arts emphasize self hypnosis and emptying the mind through deep breathing. The spiritual practices incorporated in martial arts are pagan in origin and open the doorways of our minds, allowing evil forces to come in. 

Find out how Eastern mysticism has drawn many away from the true path of Christ and has led them into darkness. This episode reminds us that we do not fight against flesh and blood but against powers and rulers of darkness.
